229
00:21:10,480 --> 00:21:13,360
Ingen fara, Paul. Du ska få medicin.

230
00:21:19,000 --> 00:21:22,600
Upp i sängen. Ett, två, tre.

231
00:21:28,240 --> 00:21:30,360
